20540 NEXT I
20550 FOR I = 1 TO 4
20560 FOR J = 1 TO 4
20570 P(I,J) = P(I,J) - (K(I,1) * P(1,J) + K(I,2) * P(2,J))
20580 NEXT J
20590 NEXT I
